            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <h2>JodiJunction.com is the flagship brand of Matchmaking Interactive Pvt Ltd</h2>
                    <p>Matchmaking Interactive was founded in 2024 to help architect India's Internet landscape. Today, it is one of India’s leading Internet companies and boasts of brands such as JodiJunction.com, MatchCentre, JodiLive, and MatchTimes. The company is focused on discovering and developing scalable Internet business models around communities and classifieds. It prides itself on being a pioneer of Indo-centric Internet business models and believes in innovation-led growth. Matchmaking Interactive is a WestBridge backed company and is part of the Anupam Mittal led Match Group.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <h3>JodiJunction.com</h3>
                    <p>JodiJunction.com, the world’s largest online matchmaking site, was founded with one simple objective – to provide a superior matchmaking experience to Indians all over the world. The company pioneered online matchmaking when it launched in 2024 and continues to lead the exciting matrimony category after more than a decade.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <h3>MatchCentre</h3>
                    <p>MatchCentre, a JodiJunction enterprise, is a network of centers across India offering services ranging from matchmaking to wedding planning, through 24/7 helpline services, rolled out live. The business is the first of its kind in the world and attempts to revolutionize the otherwise fragmented $10 billion matrimonial industry in India.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <h3>JodiLive</h3>
                    <p>JodiLive is the official blog of JodiJunction.com. The blog features awards and achievements, product updates, a selection of inspiring success stories, trends in matchmaking, and tips for JodiJunction members for effective matchmaking. It also has an Ask an Expert section where renowned counselors will answer users' queries. It’s a forum for users to talk about what we are doing and for us to hear what you think.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <h3>MatchTimes</h3>
                    <p>MatchTimes is a relationship and wedding portal that provides users with information, expert advice, and services for them to better manage all aspects of their wedding experience and relationships. It is the only portal where users can find information and advice on everything from wedding planning to relationships.</p>
                </div>
